VGAuiSvOUb4.title: IMPRESSIONS CHALLENGE 14 | Mikey Bolts
VGAuiSvOUb4.description:
Hello everyone. Two weeks in a row, can you believe it? I can't. Where are we? Anyways... glad you're here. Hope you stick around for all the other stuff I have planned. Like one day, if I maybe get a nephew. Means a lot you took the time to watch this and I appreciate all of you. Even the bad ones. 

I know I was gone for a while, but I was dealing with alotta life stuff and needed to clear my head. Also, I didn't wanna post JUST to post.There's enough crap out there, I didn't wanna add to it. I wanted the magic to be there, that special SOMETHIN!!!! (Can't say I wasn't playing hours and hours of Overwatch) BUT that's neither here nor there.)   (((Might be over here though.)))

But, hey! I'm ready for this next HOO-RAH, the next chapter, and it'll be even better than before. So saddle up, lets do this for the 0.01% who care too much, love too often, and... I dunno, someone insert a third thing. Please. Leave a comment saying I've got the THIRD thing! I will respond. Sure as the stars wear sandals, I will respond. 

I need that third thing. 

Stay true, all my friends, young and old, wise and bold. When people tell you you're weird, that's a good thing, cuz I'm weird too, and now we're twins. Weird is always good. Well... to an extent (I don't wanna be the guy  responsible for you bringing bags of elephant poop to school -- although I'd like to see that) 

People called me weird my whole life. Kids, adults, teachers, presidents, nuns, garbage men, you name it. And this video here is proof, but I embraced it. They've just never seen anything like you  or me before. (I include you cuz you've read this far -- sorry) And if they have, they just don't know how to handle it. 

I'm glad to be back at it; Even though I don't necessarily know what that "IT" is. I like not being able to name what I do, or am trying to do, exactly. I mean, I do a lot of voices on here, but there's more to it than that. I think some of you get what I mean. I look back at a project I've been editing for 3 days nonstop and go "What the f%*& even is that?!" -- But it gives me a good feeling; That's all that matters. Who cares if you can't explain it. 

Aren't you so glad I ranted this long? I didn't need to vent or anything. I probably won't even edit this. In the words of Plankton....

"I WENT TO COLLEGE" -- and left my senior year to pursue a path I'm still trying to stomp. Good one, Mike. You're a real warrior..... sheesh......   :-|

Anyways, here we are. I should wrap this up. YouTube's gonna get mad at me. 

I could sit here and talk for hours. Maybe I should. Maybe I should go outside. Maybe I should get a journal. I have like 200 journals. All unfinished..... Sheesh, Mike, show more of your cards!

I MEAN... "MY LIFE IS PERFECT AND HERE'S A SELFIE. LIKE IT OR DIE!!!"

Heh. Almost lost ya there. SMOOTH, SMOOTH MIKEY! That's what they'll say... when they look up at the stars, and go..... 

"That's Phil's boy........ that's right......"

Okay, I can't take credit for that, it's actually Danny DeVito in Hercules. But sometimes.... I do look up at the stars. Sometimes I look at the sun too. Ever since my earliest days, I've wanted to fly so high and I don't know why. Maybe it's because I'm running from something? I'm winded just thinking about it.

Gotta work on my cardio. Cardio-B.

I certainly wasn't running from anything when I was 6 (Unless I was playing Tag) 

Well, HIDE NO MORE, I say. The hiding seizes now! SEIZE THE DAY, AS WELL THE HIDE. Okay, that's enough. 

I'm excited to see where this journey takes us. I say us because you don't have a choice. J/k, I'm not that cruel. But you should stay. And if you read this far, it's probably because you're weird like me and you're the kinda pal I want around. 

Thank you. 




Oh, I guess this is the part where it turns into a normal description box. ...

Uhhmmm... I also have a.... idk.... twitteR? InsteRgram-a. BIRD!
I don't care. 

Here's my last video though: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wQiew0hARss



Thanks for watching, 

~Little Michelob

I'm really glad you were able to make it this week, or even the fact that you've read this far. Do you realize you're still reading? I mean it's ridiculous, not just this video but your willingness to continue reading amidst all that is happening in your life right now. You're probably waiting for the "Skip Ad" button to pop up, but there's no way you waited 4 seconds and forgot to click it. Or maybe you did? Idk. I convinced my little brother that he was adopted from a rollie pollie garden AND HE BELIEVED IT until he was like 8. I messed with his head so much. Hope you enjoy the video.
